                <h1>What's Running in the Background on Your Phone?</h1>
                <p>Running in the background on your phone refers to various apps and processes that continue to operate without being actively used. These may include social media notifications, music playback, or system updates. Managing background apps can enhance performance, conserve battery life, and protect privacy by minimizing data usage.</p>
